                        "name": "robo47",
                        "displayName": "Benjamin Steininger",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Setting it to 0 by default allows things like searches for * AND * AND * (and longer) which allows each user to easily let the script run for a long time and consume lots of  memory until memory_limit or max_execution_time is reached.\n\nI think security here should come first to not allow those things if the user not explicitly wants it.",
